WEBVTT

00:00.001 --> 00:05.544
synced and corrected
by peritta

00:05.546 --> 00:07.385
<i>Previously, on
"Hap and Leonard."</i>

00:07.416 --> 00:08.250
You found the car!

00:08.410 --> 00:10.210
We'll take the money from the heist

00:10.300 --> 00:12.099
and start the corporation.

00:12.100 --> 00:14.088
You're gonna need to
bring your guns with you.

00:14.090 --> 00:15.707
Thought you didn't like my guns.

00:15.709 --> 00:17.655
<i>Police still have
no clues in the brutal murder--</i>

00:17.657 --> 00:18.500
Ugh!

00:18.501 --> 00:20.799
This whole town's
gonna be swarming with police.

00:20.800 --> 00:21.932
<i>Let's do this.</i>

00:23.632 --> 00:25.064
Shh-shh-shh.

00:25.233 --> 00:27.432
I'm lookin' for an answer, sugar.

00:27.434 --> 00:28.930
I just wanna be with you.

00:28.932 --> 00:29.766
Just you.

00:29.889 --> 00:31.720
We're takin' all the money.

00:31.722 --> 00:33.221
<i>If you try and stop us...</i>

00:33.228 --> 00:34.428
<i>We'll kill you.</i>

